<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to Alphabeta: Empowering Learning & Sustainable Living</h1>
        <p>Fostering innovation, sustainability, and growth through collaborative projects and digital learning resources</p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="#about">About Us</a>
        <a href="#projects">Our Projects</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero">
        <h2>Building a Community for Lifelong Learning & Green Solutions</h2>
        <p>Join us in creating a future where knowledge, sustainability, and community thrive together. Explore our projects and contribute to real-world solutions.</p>
    </div>

    <BooksList />

    <section class="section" id="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>Alphabeta is a forward-thinking organization that blends <strong>Digital Learning Resources</strong> with <strong>Sustainability-Driven Projects</strong> to empower communities. We aim to provide individuals with tools and knowledge that enable them to solve real-world problems, from tackling urban heat and air pollution to fostering personal growth through education.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="projects">
        <h2>Our Projects</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Digital Library</strong>: Access a growing collection of educational resources focused on sustainability, innovation, and community building.</li>
            <li><strong>Climate Impact Explorer</strong>: A digital tool providing insights into the local impact of climate change on natural resources. Using data science and open data, it empowers individuals to make informed decisions and track their contributions to climate action.</li>
            <li><strong>Connected Planters</strong>: Planters equipped with sensors to monitor environmental data. The data collected helps urban farmers optimize plant care and supports real-time climate insights.</li>
            <li><strong>Farmers' Digital Hub</strong>: A platform for local farmers to upload crop data and receive personalized recommendations to improve yields and sustainability.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="business-model">
        <h2>Our Business Model</h2>
        <p>Alphabeta operates as a <strong>for-profit, community-driven enterprise</strong>. Our goal is to create sustainable, impactful solutions that are financially viable and socially beneficial. We reinvest a portion of our profits into educational initiatives and community projects, ensuring that everyone involved benefits from our success.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="get-involved">
        <h2>Get Involved</h2>
        <p>We're looking for partners, volunteers, and contributors to join us in creating a more sustainable, equitable world. Whether you want to help grow our digital library, contribute to environmental projects, or attend our workshops, there's a place for you at Alphabeta.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="contact">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Have questions or want to support our mission? Reach out to us at:</p>
        <p>Email: singh.gurprit@outlook.com | Phone: +1-438-722-3299</p>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Alphabeta. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <div id="chatbot">
        <header>Ask Alphabeta!</header>
        <div id="chatbot-messages"></div>
        <div id="chatbot-input">
            <input type="text" id="user-input" placeholder="Type your question here...">
            <button onClick={sendMessage}>Send</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <button id="chatbot-toggle" onClick={toggleChatbot}>&#128172;</button>
</body>
